      CREATE (a)-[:REL]->(b),
             (b)-[:REL]->(c),
             (c)-[:REL]->(d),
             (a)-[:X {blocked: true}]->(x),
             (x)-[:X {blocked: true}]->(d)
      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH p = shortestPath((src:A)-[*]->(dst:D))
