      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH p = allShortestPaths((start:START)-[*]->(end:END))
      WHERE ALL(x in relationships(p) WHERE x.p IS NOT NULL)
      RETURN length(p) AS len
      """
    Then the result should be, in order:
      | len |
      |  3  |
    And no side effects

